Individual names Michael Kolowic chairman . Individual Inc said Thursday that Michael Kolowich , president and chief executive officer , has also been namded chairman of the board . He replaces former Chairman Andy Devereaux , who will continue as an active member on the board of directors . Prior to joining Individual in September 1996 , Kolowich was president and founder of AT & T Corp ' s AT & T New Media Services , where he led the development of information services for business professionals . Individual is a provider of electronic personalized business information services . Through its exclusive information retrieval , filtering , and delivery technologies , Individual brings targeted business news , information , and advertising to 560 , 000 readers . 
